title: Amazon BSR Explained - What Is Best Seller Rank?
description:
The amazon best seller ranking is simple: the smaller the number, the more it's selling. But that's not everything - this number is fluid and changes every hour. So you need to look at the long term average rank to get the best data.

Questions? Comment below and I'll do my best to answer them.
